As a user, I want the inventory to have images and product description, so that it enhances accuracy and overall user-esperience.
As a user, I want the system to introduce dashboards with simple interface , so that I can easily navigate from one place to another.
As a user, I want the ability to search for specific inventory items using keywords, so that I can find the informtaion I need efficiently.
As a user, I want the system to have robust security feautures such as user factor authetication , so that it protects sensitive inventory data.
As a user, I want the system to provide historical data, so that I can track my previous orders.
